            Boca Juniors v River Plate final in Copa Libertadores postponed after team bus attacked.
            Clashes between Boca Juniors and River Plate have delayed the second leg of a Copa Libertadores cup final match after the former team's bus was attacked.Boca Junior players on the bus were injured in the incident between two of Argentina's biggest rivals.
                
                        25 Nov 2018
                    
                
        
